snippet.title: Sports Champions 2 - Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
The sequel to the most popular Playstation Move title is back! Sports Champions 2 is coming, and will feature all-new sports such as skiing, tennis, boxing, golf, bowling, and updated archery!

Sports Champions 2 - Coming this Fall
